            bindings = <
          &kp Q               &kp W           &kp F           &kp P        &kp B           &kp J           &kp L            &kp U              &kp Y            &kp SINGLE_QUOTE
          &mt LEFT_CONTROL A  &mt LEFT_ALT R  &mt LEFT_WIN S  &mt LSHFT T  &kp G           &kp M           &mt RSHFT N      &mt RIGHT_GUI E    &mt RIGHT_ALT I  &mt RIGHT_CONTROL O
&kp CAPS  &kp Z               &kp X           &kp C           &kp D        &kp V           &kp K           &kp H            &kp COMMA          &kp DOT          &kp FSLH             &kp SEMICOLON
                                              &sk LEFT_ALT    &lt 3 SPACE  &sk LEFT_GUI    &sk LEFT_SHIFT  &lt 1 BACKSPACE  &sk RIGHT_CONTROL
